company_website.summary: Wildseed is a craft manufacturing and distribution facility in Arcata, CA. They produce a variety of cannabis products including oils and vapes, as well as natural skincare and beauty products.
company_website.infomration_about_the_team: The key executives and decision makers at Wildseed, LLC appear to be Michael Mclaren and Pawel Rudnicki, who are listed as the business owners. However, I was unable to find detailed contact information or LinkedIn profiles for these individuals.

executives.name: Michael Mclaren
executives.customer_note: Michael Mclaren is listed as a business owner of Wildseed, LLC. He can be contacted at the email address Michael@wildseedoil.Com.

executives.name: Pawel Rudnicki
executives.customer_note: Pawel Rudnicki is listed as a business owner of Wildseed, LLC.
